OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,FSaturday evening with isolated
OL,7,Fthundery showers clearing. Cloud
OL,8,Fincreasing to bring a few showers from
OL,9,Fthe west overnight. Temperatures
OL,10,Fremaining warm overnight. Winds
OL,11,Fsouthwesterly and mostly light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FFresher conditions spreading
OL,14,Fto all parts into Sunday, with
OL,15,Fsunshine and showers. More seasonable
OL,16,Ftemperatures than expected. Winds
OL,17,Fmoderate southwesterly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
