OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fis looking dry and settled. Turning
OL,7,Fmore unsettled on Tuesday with
OL,8,Fsunshine and showers. Wednesday starts
OL,9,Fof sunny, then clouding over with rain
OL,10,Flater.
